---
// Console — terminal animation showing memory recall example
---

<aside class="console" aria-label="Memory recall example">
  <div class="console-top"><span>agent-memory-loop</span><span class="status">online</span></div>
  <pre class="terminal terminal-animated"><span class="tl" style="--d:0"><span class="muted">$</span> resolve_reasoning("Next.js hydration mismatch")
<span class="ok">hit</span> FC-002
<span class="muted">root cause</span> server/client render drift</span><span class="tl" style="--d:1">
<span class="muted">$</span> check_failures("add suppressHydrationWarning")
<span class="warn">risk</span> masks symptom; root cause still unknown</span><span class="tl" style="--d:2">
<span class="muted">$</span> verify_first("compare server HTML vs client DOM")
<span class="ok">next</span> fix deterministic render source</span></pre>
  <div class="console-grid">
    <div class="console-step"><b>1. Search</b><p>Find existing reasoning before spending fresh tokens.</p></div>
    <div class="console-step"><b>2. Verify</b><p>Check risky approaches against known failure patterns.</p></div>
    <div class="console-step"><b>3. Reuse</b><p>Store the verified fix so the next agent starts smarter.</p></div>
  </div>
</aside>

<style>
  .console {
    background: var(--code);
    color: var(--code-text);
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    position: sticky;
    top: 24px;
  }

  .console-top {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 12px 18px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.04);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--faint);
  }

  .console-top .status {
    color: #4ade80;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .terminal {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 20px;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    white-space: pre-wrap;
    word-break: break-word;
    overflow: auto;
    max-height: 320px;
  }

  .terminal .muted { color: var(--faint); }
  .terminal .ok { color: #4ade80; font-weight: 700; }
  .terminal .warn { color: #fbbf24; font-weight: 700; }

  .terminal-animated .tl {
    display: block;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: terminal-reveal .5s ease forwards;
    animation-delay: calc(var(--d) * 1.2s);
  }

  @keyframes terminal-reveal {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(6px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .console-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
  }

  .console-step {
    padding: 16px 18px;
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  .console-step + .console-step {
    border-left: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
  }

  .console-step b {
    display: block;
    color: var(--code-text);
    font-size: 13px;
    margin-bottom: 9px;
  }

  .console-step p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--faint);
    font-size: 12.5px;
    line-height: 1.66;
  }

  @media (max-width: 980px) {
    .console-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .console-step + .console-step {
      border-left: 0;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
    }
  }
</style>
